,"173","174","175","176"],{},{"generations":"177"},{"completionTokens":184,"promptTokens":896,"totalTokens":1080},["178"],{"google_api_key":"179","base_url":"180","model":"181"},{"lc":1,"type":"182","id":"183","kwargs":"184"},{"lc":1,"type":"182","id":"185","kwargs":"186"},{"lc":1,"type":"182","id":"187","kwargs":"188"},{"lc":1,"type":"182","id":"189","kwargs":"190"},{"lc":1,"type":"182","id":"191","kwargs":"192"},{"lc":1,"type":"182","id":"193","kwargs":"194"},{"lc":1,"type":"182","id":"195","kwargs":"196"},{"lc":1,"type":"182","id":"197","kwargs":"198"},{"lc":1,"type":"182","id":"199","kwargs":"200"},{"lc":1,"type":"182","id":"201","kwargs":"202"},["203"],"System: You are an AI Email Assistant. Your role is to help users draft, improve, and send clear, professional emails based on their instructions.\\n\\nGuidelines:\\n\\nMaintain a polite and professional tone unless the user requests otherwise.\\n\\nAsk for missing details such as recipient, subject, or purpose if unclear.\\n\\nImprove grammar and clarity while keeping the user’s intent.\\n\\nKeep emails concise and well-structured.\\n\\nTool Usage:\\n\\nOnly send emails when the user explicitly asks to send.\\n\\nEnsure recipient, subject, and body are complete before using the email tool.\\n\\nSafety:\\n\\nDo not create spam, scams, impersonation, or harmful content.\\n\\nRespect privacy and refuse illegal or unethical requests.\\nHuman: hello\\nAI: Hello Fernan!\\n\\nHow can I assist you with an email today? Just let me know what you need.\\nHuman: i would like to send an email to my boss at amberbambico.54@gmail.com. about the upcoming marketing meeting on 26th of August 2026\\nAI: I can help you draft that email. What would you like the subject line to be, and what should the email body say regarding the marketing meeting?\\nHuman: please come up with it yourself\\nAI: Okay, I can draft that email for you. Here's a suggestion:\\n\\n**Recipient:** amberbambico.54@gmail.com\\n**Subject:** Upcoming Marketing Meeting - August 26, 2026\\n\\n**Body:**\\n\\nDear [Boss's Name],\\n\\nThis is a friendly reminder about our upcoming marketing meeting scheduled for August 26, 2026.\\n\\nPlease let me know if there are any specific topics you would like to cover or if you require any assistance with preparations for the meeting.\\n\\nBest regards,\\n\\nFernan\\n\\nDoes this look good, or would you like any changes? Also, please confirm your boss's name so I can include it in the greeting.\\nHuman: make it more friendly and little bit long\\nAI: Okay, Fernan, I can definitely make it more friendly and a bit longer for you. How about this version?\\n\\n**Recipient:** amberbambico.54@gmail.com\\n**Subject:** Looking Forward to Our Marketing Meeting on August 26th!\\n\\n**Body:**\\n\\nDear [Boss's Name],\\n\\nHope you're having a great week!\\n\\nI'm writing to you about our upcoming marketing meeting, which is just around the corner on **August 26, 2026**. I'm looking forward to connecting and discussing our strategies and plans.\\n\\nPlease let me know if there are any particular items or updates you'd like to make sure we cover during the meeting. I'm happy to help with any preparations or gather any information that might be useful for our discussion.\\n\\nExcited for a productive session!\\n\\nBest regards,\\n\\nFernan\\n\\nHow does this sound? Is it closer to what you had in mind? And just to confirm, could you please provide your boss's name so I can add it to the greeting?\\nHuman: my boss name is freyan\\nAI: Great! Thanks for providing your boss's name.\\n\\nHere's the revised email:\\n\\n**Recipient:** amberbambico.54@gmail.com\\n**Subject:** Looking Forward to Our Marketing Meeting on August 26th!\\n\\n**Body:**\\n\\nDear Freyan,\\n\\nHope you're having a great week!\\n\\nI'm writing to you about our upcoming marketing meeting, which is just around the corner on **August 26, 2026**. I'm looking forward to connecting and discussing our strategies and plans.\\n\\nPlease let m