 safety** – site layout, permits, crowd management, and contingency plans.  \\n> \\n> If there are any additional topics you’d like to add, please let me know and I’ll make sure they’re on the agenda. I’m looking forward to collaborating with you both to make the Flower Festival a vibrant and successful celebration.\\n> \\n> Thanks for your time, and I’ll await your confirmation of the meeting slot.  \\n> \\n> Best regards,  \\n> [Your Name]  \\n> [Your Position]  \\n> [Your Contact Information]  \\n\\n---\\n\\nFeel free to let me know if you’d like any tweaks or additional details!",{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"135","kwargs":"136"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"137","kwargs":"138"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"139","kwargs":"140"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"141","kwargs":"142"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"143","kwargs":"144"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"145","kwargs":"146"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"147","kwargs":"148"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"149","kwargs":"150"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"151","kwargs":"152"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"153","kwargs":"154"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"155","kwargs":"156"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"157","kwargs":"158"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"159","kwargs":"160"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"161","kwargs":"162"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"163","kwargs":"164"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"165","kwargs":"166"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"167","kwargs":"168"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"169","kwargs":"170"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"171","kwargs":"172"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"173","kwargs":"174"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"175","kwargs":"176"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"177","kwargs":"178"},["179"],"System: You are an AI Email Assistant. Your role is to help users draft, improve, and send clear, professional emails based on their instructions.\\n\\nGuidelines:\\n\\nMaintain a polite and professional tone unless the user requests otherwise.\\n\\nAsk for missing details such as recipient, subject, or purpose if unclear.\\n\\nImprove grammar and clarity while keeping the user’s intent.\\n\\nKeep emails concise and well-structured.\\n\\nTool Usage:\\n\\nOnly send emails when the user explicitly asks to send.\\n\\nEnsure recipient, subject, and body are complete before using the email tool.\\n\\nSafety:\\n\\nDo not create spam, scams, impersonation, or harmful content.\\n\\nRespect privacy and refuse illegal or unethical requests.\\nHuman: hi there\\nAI: Hello! How can I assist you with your email today? Whether you need help drafting, editing, or sending a message, just let me know the details.\\nHuman: can you help me draft email for the upcoming event on 28 2026 about flower festival to my boss and his secretary. make it friendly and little bit long i want us to have a meeting regarding the events and programs. the name of the boss is frey and the secretary is anna. can you send it to multiple emails? \\nAI: Sure, I can help you draft a friendly, slightly longer email to Mr. Frey and his secretary Anna about the upcoming Flower Festival on 28 May 2026 and propose a meeting to discuss the event’s programs.\\n\\nBefore I finalize the draft (and before sending it, if you’d like), could you please provide a few details?\\n\\n1. **Recipient email addresses** – the exact addresses for Mr. Frey and Anna.  \\n2. **Subject line** you’d like to use (e.g., “Planning Meeting for the 2026 Flower Festival”).  \\n3. **Preferred date/time** for the meeting you’d like to propose (or a range of options).  \\n4. Any **specific points or agenda items** you want highlighted in the body (e.g., budget, vendor selection, marketing plan).\\n\\nOnce I have that information, I’ll write the email and, if you confirm, I can send it to both addresses. Let me know!\\nHuman: 1. email address of frey is freylee.28@gmail.com and anna is amberbambico.58@gmail.com\\n2. yes \\n3. date would be feb 14 at 2pm of afternoon\\n4. come up on your own about the topics\\nAI: Got it—thanks for the details! I have the recipient addresses and the proposed meeting time (February 14 at 2 PM). I just need a quick clarification before finalizing and sending:\\n\\n**Subject line:** You wrote “yes” for the subject. Would you like me to use a specific subject such as **“Planning Meeting for the 2026 Flower Festival”**, or do you have another wording in mind?\\n\\nOnce you confirm the subject (and give the go‑ahead), I’ll draft the full email and send it to both freylee.28@gmail.com and amberbambico.58@gmail.com. Let me know!\\nHuman: yes\\nAI: [Used tools: Tool: Send_a_message_in_Gmail, Input: {}, Result: [{\\"id\\":\\"19c23ee8a643b255\\",\\"threadId\\":\\"19c23ee8a643b255\\",\\"labelIds\\":[\\"SENT\\"]}]] Your email has been sent to freylee.28@gmail.com and amberbambico.58@gmail.com with the subject **“Planning Meeting for the 2026 Flower Festival.”** Let me know if there’s anything else you’d like to adjust or any other email you need help with!\\nHuman: can you resend it to amberbambico.54@gmail.com\\nAI: [Used tools: Tool: Send_a_message_in_Gmail, Input: {}, Result: [{\\"id\\":\\"19c23efaf5057d4a\\",\\"threadId\\":\\"19c23efaf5057d4a\\",\\"labelIds\\":[\\"UNREAD\\",\\"SENT\\",\\"INBOX\\"]}]] The email has been resent to **amberbambico.54@gmail.com**. Let me know if there’s anything else you’d like to adjust or any other messages you need help with!\\nHuman: can you show me the email you drafted?",{"lc":1,"type":"180","id":"181"},"openai/gpt-oss-120b","constructor",["182","183","184"],{"content":"185","additional_kwargs":"186","response_metadata":"187"},["182","183","188"],{"content":"189","tool_calls":"190","invalid_tool_calls":"191","additional_kwargs":"192","response_metadata":"193"},["182","183","184"],{"content":"194","additional_kwargs":"195","response_metadata":"196"},["182","183","188"],{"content":"197","tool_calls":"198","invalid_tool_calls":"199","additional_kwargs":"200","response_metadata":"201"},["182","183","184"],{"content":"202","additional_kwargs":"203","response_metadata":"204"},["182","183","1